Text: Read more …  AbbVie Inc (NYSE:ABBV) Vice Chairman Laura J. Schumacher purchased 25,000 shares of the stock in a transaction dated Monday, September 16th. The stock was bought at an average cost of $70.42 per share, with a total value of $1,760,500.00. Following the transaction, the insider now owns 164,838 shares in the company, valued at $11,607,891.96.
